mb|P|mb|2S|NT|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Had north bid 2@D, I want to show my 5-card heart suit to see if we have a 5-3 heart fit. Some people play a confusing convention called |CP|1|FP|2|AT|^*Hhttp://www.bridgeguys.com/Conventions/smolen_convention.html,Smolen^*N|CP||FP||at| which I will explain in a second. But if playing natural bidding, I would bid 3@H over 2@D and partner would bid 4@H with 3-card support or 3NT otherwise.|
